Method Detail

addBranch

void addBranch(InitializerFlow initialBranch,
               FinalizerFlow finalBranch)
Adds a new branch starting in initialBranch and finishing in finalBranch. The entry point is linked to the initialBranch whereas the final Branch is linked to the exit point.

Parameters:
initialBranch - First step of the internal branch
finalBranch - Last step of the internal branch

addBranch

void addBranch(TaskFlow branch)
Adds a new branch consisting of a unique flow. The branch has the entry point as predecessor and the exit point as successor.

Parameters:
branch - A unique flow defining an internal branch
